                <th scope="col" class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-ink-50 bg-geo-900/60">Content Format</th>
                <th scope="col" class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-ink-50 bg-geo-900/60">GEO Priority</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/[.02]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-200 font-medium">Definitional</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-300">"What is a lasting power of attorney"</td>
