                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-200 font-medium">Comparative</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-300">"Best employment solicitors London"</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-300">Entity authority + directory presence</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-yellow-400">Medium</td>
